{"tid":2442540,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英媒︰中國科興疫苗有效對抗巴西發現的變異新冠病毒","createTime":"2021-03-11T12:02:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T12:32:33.000Z","uid":85180,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"180c6b07652ce910964edb55d545b23d0b2e7d9a","tid":2442540,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T12:02:20.000Z","msg":"英媒︰中國科興疫苗有效對抗巴西發現的變異新冠病毒<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.81.cn/big5/ss/attachement/jpg/site351/20210311/6c4b9041ab8b21b333dc01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.81.cn%2Fbig5%2Fss%2Fattachement%2Fjpg%2Fsite351%2F20210311%2F6c4b9041ab8b21b333dc01.jpg&h=97effb2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">球王比利接種科興疫苗。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n海外網3月9日電 英國路透社周一（8日）報道稱，根據巴西一項研究的初步數據，中國科興的新冠疫苗對巴西發現的P1變異新冠病毒有效。<br />\n<br />\n報道援引熟悉巴西這項研究的消息人士稱，中國科興生物研發的新冠疫苗對首次在巴西發現的病毒P1變異新冠病毒有效。報道指出，研究人員對已接種疫苗者的血液進行檢測，發現疫苗有效對抗P1變異新冠病毒。<br />\n<br />\n巴西已經在全國展開新冠疫苗接種。中國疫苗的到來為當地抗疫提供了支持，科興疫苗目前是巴西采用的主要疫苗，巴西衛生部早前曾表明，科興疫苗對在英國及南非首次發現的變異新冠病毒同樣有效。"},{"pid":"02873514d669af12f5d9cda77c694fe1f1d33b27","tid":2442540,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T12:04:18.000Z","msg":"路透社<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2007年5月15日，加拿大湯姆森集團和路透集團發表聲明，就合併事宜達成一致。交易價值為172億美元。[6]湯姆森現在控制著大約53％的新公司，新公司名為湯森路透。新的首席湯姆&middot;格羅瑟，曾持路透社早先的15％的股份。2008年3月26日，這兩個機構的股東同意合併。"},{"pid":"12f46fd80ba3785fecc81a1f58913b1967c97f74","tid":2442540,"uid":271250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T12:05:40.000Z","msg":"如果比利死咗，tvb會唔會播返佢d經典賽事？"},{"pid":"ffbca7eb4c2dcd4f5a7aa10ae3d1eeeb196e2968","tid":2442540,"uid":37586,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T12:07:31.000Z","msg":"有效1%定11%<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16c970791a7f036043edf74d6c2a3e41f7ce947a","tid":2442540,"uid":9542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T12:09:17.000Z","msg":"巴西呢期好紅，日日爆到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56b6767ff6acb8e3fa9510dbf61b183433a83899","tid":2442540,"uid":387826,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T12:11:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ACgOXrW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FACgOXrW.png&h=c6dde8ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"67e70ff0d66f82bf40a5e49233a6666ac5823de1","tid":2442540,"uid":156573,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"56b6767ff6acb8e3fa9510dbf61b183433a83899","tid":2442540,"uid":387826,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T12:11:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ACgOXrW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FACgOXrW.png&h=c6dde8ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T12:13:38.000Z","msg":"pk 笑咗，要落地獄了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7381d2205f441922bea76649bcf9d5abe4db98ec","tid":2442540,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T12:13:54.000Z","msg":"［你諗你］以色列健康部同輝瑞、BioMTech研究發現 復必泰喺現實應用嘅有效率達97%<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2442559\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2442559</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b65b3b4fb16f65f4368492d11e374bd6e8581a3c","tid":2442540,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T12:20:24.000Z","msg":"又比左幾多錢稿費"},{"pid":"4a72739ac4ecaccc6f5301274c94831e3625384d","tid":2442540,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T12:23:08.000Z","msg":"科興本身就係變異新病毒"},{"pid":"c4f21370fd1f34b27d8d4ac3695cb1f3cf5bc1a6","tid":2442540,"uid":2087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s